- Sent an email to Lily (lily.white@gmail.com) requesting the book list and asking her to attach or provide a direct link to the first book. I also mentioned the tentative meeting time and asked for her availability.

If you'd like, I can:
- Retry downloading the book if you provide an alternate link or if Lily replies with one.
- Add Lily (or other participants) to the calendar event once you give me their emails.
- Move the meeting time or add a location/agenda to the event.
